Pre-Apocalypse[]: Nothing is known about Wayne's life prior to or as the outbreak began.
Post-Apocalypse[]: In a flashback four months prior, Wayne was camping in the woods with a group of survivors when they rescued a man named Dante from walkers . Sometime later, the group is encountered by the Alexandrians and are recruited to join the community . Wayne and Jen are interviewed by the Council following Siddiq 's death to know more about Dante's behavior during his time with their group prior to their arrival at the community. Following Beta 's attack on Alexandria that left several Alexandrians dead, Wayne has not been seen or mentioned since, leaving his fate unknown.
